{{Italic title}}
'''''Energy''''' is a [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] covering research on [[energy engineering]] that was established in 1976. It is published by [[Elsevier]] and the [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Henrik Lund (academic)|Henrik Lund]] ([[Aalborg University]]). According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2013 [[impact factor]] of  4.159, ranking it 13th out of 83 journals in the category "Energy & Fuels"<ref name=WoS1>{{cite book |year=2014 |chapter=Journals Ranked by Impact: Energy & Fuels |title=2013 [[Journal Citation Reports]] |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web of Science]]}}</ref> and second out of 55 journals in "Thermodynamics".<ref name=WoS2>{{cite book |year=2014 |chapter=Journals Ranked by Impact: Thermodynamics |title=2013 [[Journal Citation Reports]] |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web of Science]]}}</ref>

